column5: Great location 2 mi. north of TWU/University Dr.; 3 mi. from Denton Town Square; 3 mi. to Water Works. Two bedrooms at one end of the house are available for rent with a bathroom in between. If the other one is not rented, you'll have a private bath. Bed is about a year old and seldom used. I work from home, so I will be here most of the time. Neighborhood is quiet. I have 2 rooms for rent; the other has a queen bed.
column8: Twin bed/desk; near everything; quiet neighborhood
